<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>196</hymn_number>
<title>KHUARUAHHAR NUNNAK BIA CH196</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hla in ka sinah run chim tuah, Khuaruahhar nun nak bia, An i dawhnak
 ka hmuh ter tuah, Khuaruahhar nunnak bia, Nunnak bia dawh bik cu a
 zumhning ka cawnpiak.

[C1]
   (A dawh bik bia, khuaruahhar bia, Zungzal nunnak bia kha, A dawh bik
   bia, khuaruahhar bia, Zungzal nunnak bia kha)2.

[V2]
 Jesuh nih mikip a pek hna, Khuaruahhar nunnak bia, Misual, a aw nem
 ngai tuah u, Khuaruahhar nunnak bia, Man lo-in a kan pek vancung a kan
 tlunter.

[C2]
   (A dawh bik bia, khuaruahhar bia, Zungzal nunnak bia kha, A dawh bik
   bia, khuaruahhar bia, Zungzal nunnak bia kha)2.

[V3]
 Dawh in a thang lai Thawngthabia, Khuaruahhar nunnak bia,
 Ngaihthiamnak mikip a pek hna, Khuaruahhar nunnak bia, Jesuh a kan
 Khamhtu kannih kan thianter tuah.

[C3]
   (A dawh bik bia, khuaruahhar bia, Zungzal nunnak bia kha, A dawh bik
   bia, khuaruahhar bia, Zungzal nunnak bia kha)2.</lyrics>
</song>